Hablamemo
----------

Description
-----------
Increase your memory skills while learning a new language. Create a vocabulary kvtml file (e.g. in Parley), load it to Hablamemo, select your level and you are ready! Image mode is also supported.


Dependencies
------------
- Plasma 5.0 or later

//TODO: Update after 15.10 testing

Installation
------------
- Add Widgets... -> Get new widgets -> Download new plasma widgets


